//chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-29-at-上午10.47.50.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-10-29 at 上午10.47.50\" width=\"423\" height=\"450\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-416218\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-29-at-上午10.47.50.png 423w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-29-at-上午10.47.50-282x300.png 282w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 423px) 100vw, 423px\" /></a></p></blockquote>\n","author":996,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,17016],"tags":[29083,29082,23757,29053,29049,10710,26991,18979,9897,21528,9362]}